WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.142
A white-clad female ghost glides through iron bars toward a terrified man.

2
00:00:09.102 --> 00:00:13.062
The ghost advances, her long white costume flowing in the dim light.

3
00:00:14.072 --> 00:00:25.592
Zhang Peizan backs against the wall as the ghost closes in. Her face is hidden in shadow. He is trapped with no way to escape.

4
00:00:33.475 --> 00:00:36.572
Her ghostly white face is suddenly revealed.

5
00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:52.925
The door slams shut, sealing Zhang inside.

6
00:00:56.509 --> 00:01:04.000
Zhang falls to both knees, hands clasped, desperately begging the ghost for mercy.

7
00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:07.689
Zhang kneels on the floor, cowering below her.

8
00:01:27.594 --> 00:01:32.800
The ghost leans close; Zhang gazes up from the floor in fear.

9
00:01:43.125 --> 00:01:47.700
The ghost pursues Zhang in frantic circles, demanding confession.

10
00:01:59.042 --> 00:02:04.282
Judge Bao appears above; Qianjin removes her disguise. Zhang collapses.
